U.confirm
U.save!And the user is ready to login

'code is art' was a quote I saw on the WordPress site. Arts sole purpose is itself ergo any piece of useful code is by definition not art. another perspective would code is more art than science. which would really only be applicable to the underlying function. maybe they meant looking at code is pleasant which maybe true for the obfuscated C code entries that look like ascii art. the algorithm implemented maybe elegant but that's independent from the code anyway.
